  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bc7 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b95\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bc1-\u0b95\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Issuance of passports to pre-booked persons only - Notification of Immigration and Citizenship Department",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Department of Immigration and Emigration said that passports will be distributed in the coming days only to those who have made reservations based on the date and time.",
        "This decision has been taken in view of the threat of corona infection which is spreading again in the country.",
        "However, the department also said that a special one-day service has been launched for those who are going abroad urgently.",
        "Accordingly, the Department of Immigration and Emigration has also informed that those who want to get a passport due to urgent need can send their information to WhatsApp number 0706311711 to get the passport."
      ],
